<p><a name="References" id="References"></a></p>
<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=The_Mismeasure_of_Man&amp;action=edit&amp;section=15" title="Edit section: References">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">References</span></h2>
<div class="references-small">
<ol class="references">
<li id="cite_note-0"><b><a href="#cite_ref-0" title="">^</a></b> Stephen Jay Gould, <i>The Mismeasure of Man</i>. W.W. Norton &amp; Co., 1981, p. 20.</li>
